nodes.text: A clan of Mandalorians were were tasked by the ruthless Mand'alor Ung Kusp, to kill Jaing and bring back the Sith artifact stolen by the Unidentified Outer Rim cyberneticist during some time before the New Sith Wars. However most of them were killed by an enraged Durge during the fighting, this event would cause him go out and try kill the Mand'alor. Like most within the room, they were unaware they played in a plot to cause a war between the Mandalorians and the Sith.
